  - id: prioritization-guide
    title: Prioritization Guidelines
    criteria[4]{criterion,description}:
      Dependencies,What blocks what - required work must come first
      Business Value,Impact on users or business - higher value items first
      Risk,Technical uncertainty - may want to address early or defer
      Effort,Quick wins vs large efforts - balance for momentum

